These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, soy-milk
House: modern, craftsman, cape-cod, cottage
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, pakistani, french, thai
1. the malaysian is the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the french is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the thai##3
5. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
6. the thai is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
7. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
8. the thai is between the cottage house and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage         | soy-milk      | cola | fanta | milk |
| House   | cape-cod | modern  | craftsman   | cottage    |
| Nationality     | malaysian     | french    | thai    | pakistani      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, january, march
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, indie, blues, country
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, sailing, ice-hockey, baseball
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the fan of blues##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the fan of indie##1
7. the fan of d&b is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in april##2
8. the fan of country is between the fan of indie and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday         | march | january   | april | october  |
| Music-Genre   | blues     | d&b | country  | indie |
| Sport     | baseball        | ice-hockey  | sailing    | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery, fantasy, crime
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, orange, grey, brown
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, lily, aconite, amaryllis
1. the person who likes brown is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching crime movies##2
2. the person who likes orange is the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes grey is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who likes blood-red##2
7. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre          | thriller | mystery   | crime     | fantasy     |
| Color   | orange  | brown | grey   | blood-red  |
| Flower     | amaryllis      | lily | aconite | daisy |

