.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, nectarine, artichoke, kale
City: rome, hamburg, berlin, london
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, software-developer, teacher, police-officer
1. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
2. the person eating nectarine is the software-developer##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the freelancer##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
5. the person traveling to london is the freelancer##1
6. the person eating artichoke is the person traveling to rome##1
7. the person traveling to berlin is the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Food   | garlic  | kale   | artichoke     | nectarine |
| City   | berlin  | london      | rome        | hamburg     |
| Job         | teacher | freelancer | police-officer | software-developer   |

