.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, lime, pumpkin, grapefruit
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, fonseca, swisher, bongani
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, indie, electronic, dubstep
1. the person eating grapefruit is the bongani-smoker##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of trance is the bongani-smoker##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
6. the fonseca-smoker is on the far left##1
7. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
9. the pall-mall-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Food   | nectarine   | grapefruit   | pumpkin | lime |
| Cigar         | fonseca      | bongani | pall-mall      | swisher |
| Music-Genre     | indie | trance        | dubstep       | electronic  |

