.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, game, ritmeester, siglo
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, poker, billiard
House: tower, cape-cod, futuristic, victorian
1. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the person playing poker##1
3. the tower house is the game-smoker##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
6. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
7. the siglo-smoker is in an even position##4
8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar    | ritmeester   | siglo      | game       | alhambra |
| Game   | scrabble | billiard | poker     | mah-jongg |
| House     | victorian     | cape-cod  | tower | futuristic |

