.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, balloon-flower, aconite, rose
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, chestnut, emerald, light-blue
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, montecristo, dunhill
1. the montecristo-smoker is the person who likes ivory##1
2. the swisher-smoker is between the person who likes light-blue and the ritmeester-smoker##2
3. the person who likes light-blue is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
5. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
7. the person who likes ivory is the person who growsmarigold##1
8. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Flower      | aconite   | rose          | balloon-flower | marigold        |
| Color   | emerald     | chestnut | light-blue   | ivory     |
| Cigar           | ritmeester | swisher         | dunhill         | montecristo |

