.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, february, april, december
There 4 different types of food: papaya, pepper, pear, carrot
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, prince, ritmeester, pall-mall
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
2. the person eating pear is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person eating carrot is the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the prince-smoker is between the person eating papaya and the person who's birthday is in january##2
6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
7. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in april##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday         | february | january      | april       | december    |
| Food           | pepper  | pear  | carrot | papaya |
| Cigar   | pall-mall      | ritmeester | prince         | oliveros    |

