.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, polish, canadian, american
House: gothic-revival, victorian, modern, farmhouse
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, video-games, singing, rock-climbing
1. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
3. the american is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the japanese##1
5. the polish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the japanese##1
8. the victorian house is on the left of the canadian##1
9. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Nationality   | polish         | japanese  | canadian     | american         |
| House        | farmhouse | victorian | gothic-revival | modern         |
| Hobby      | video-games         | singing  | reading   | rock-climbing |

