.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, tea, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, may, april
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, amaryllis, orchid, daffodil
 1. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking juice##2
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking tea##2
10. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | juice  | tea    | milk | soy-milk    |
| Birthday   | november | may | december  | april |
| Flower           | orchid   | daffodil    | poppy        | amaryllis   |

