.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, june, may
City: new-york, hamburg, miami, berlin
There 4 different types of food: tomato, cranberry, watermelon, kiwi
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
4. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
6. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday      | october                | may  | april | june   |
| City           | berlin | hamburg | new-york   | miami |
| Food   | cranberry         | tomato     | kiwi     | watermelon |

