.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, almond-milk, sprite
4 different games are played: poker, bridge, mah-jongg, scrabble
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person driving the train is between the person playing scrabble and the person driving the skateboard##2
6. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | almond-milk    | milk  | sprite  | lemonade |
| Game   | scrabble | bridge | poker | mah-jongg |
| Transport   | quad-bike    | train     | skateboard    | jet-ski |

