.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, whist, scrabble, canasta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, family, epic, crime
House: palace, farmhouse, townhouse, tower
1. the farmhouse house is between the person playing scrabble and the person watching satire movies##2
2. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
4. the tower house is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
5. the tower house is in an odd position##4
6. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
7. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
8. the person watching epic movies is the person playing backgammon##1
9. the person watching crime movies is between the townhouse house and the palace house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Game      | backgammon | scrabble      | whist  | canasta    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | family | crime | satire |
| House           | tower      | townhouse       | farmhouse   | palace      |

