.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, snake, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, snowmobile, roller
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily, bellflower, amaryllis
1. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the horse and the person who growspoppy##2
3. the person who growslily is on the far left or far right##3
4. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the person driving the roller is between the person who growspoppy and the person driving the van##2
7. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
9. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Pet         | goldfish    | snake | ferret  | horse  |
| Transport   | snowmobile | airplane       | roller | van |
| Flower         | bellflower   | poppy      | amaryllis | lily       |

