.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, rat, frog, guinea-pig
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, manager, software-developer, lawyer
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, yellow, apricot, blue
1. the manager is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes turquise is between the person who likes yellow and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
3. the lawyer is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
4. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
6. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
7. the person who likes apricot is on the far left or far right##3
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Pet          | rat | guinea-pig  | bird   | frog    |
| Job   | photographer  | software-developer     | lawyer | manager |
| Color   | apricot   | blue | turquise | yellow   |

