4. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the siglo-smoker is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growsdaisy##2
6. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
8. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Cigar    | aristoff    | siglo    | davidoff  | baccarat |
| Flower   | azalea | tulip | daisy | daffodil      |
